
Ranger Help for: stats
======================

SUMMARY:    
If Rangers are one thing, they are balanced. Rangers do not train in just
one area of the mind or body. They have to be tough in all aspects to be
successful. Almost all of the stats will be used in one way or the other,
one skill or the other. All Rangers will benefit from training the physical
stats, such as strength, dexterity, and constitution, for obvious reasons.
However, the most important stat is wisdom. Lacking formal training, a
Ranger depends on his or her wisdom to keep them alive and breathing.
Having said that though, if you think a skill might use a stat in some way,
it probably does, so it won't hurt to raise any stat. 

=============================================================================
